trans-unit.source: Creates a panel that is associated with a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.SplitContainer" />.
trans-unit.target: Crea un panel que está asociado con una clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.SplitContainer" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SplitterPanel> is a member of its associated <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SplitContainer> rather than being a member of the underlying form.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SplitterPanel> es un miembro de su asociado <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SplitContainer> en lugar de ser un miembro del formulario subyacente.

trans-unit.source: At design time, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SplitterPanel> is accessible through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SplitContainer.Panel1%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SplitContainer.Panel2%2A> properties of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SplitContainer>.
trans-unit.target: En tiempo de diseño, el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SplitterPanel> es accesible a través del <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SplitContainer.Panel1%2A> o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SplitContainer.Panel2%2A> propiedades de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SplitContainer>.
